[1;37mdeinit[0m

[37mRemove the mango repository metadata (the .mango folder) from a directory after confirming the deletion. Defaults to the current working tree.[0m

[32m- Deinitialize the repository in the current directory:[0m
        [33mmango @deinit[0m

[32m- Deinitialize a repository at another path:[0m
        [33mmango @deinit[0m [37m~/old-project[0m